# Mark all binary files as such to prevent line-ending conversions that
# turn a 9135-byte fixture into a 0-byte / different-sized blob in
# cross-platform clones. The test-fixtures/*.sb3 entries are in
# particular susceptible because they look like text to core.autocrlf
# (they start with the PK ZIP header bytes, but whitespace inside the
# zip can still be touched).
*.sb3 binary
